    "After entries close, one winner is selected uniformly at random across all entries. The winner is notified via in-app notification and the email address on their Futpools account within 48 hours. Winner has 7 days to claim the prize; unclaimed prizes are forfeit.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "After entries close, one winner is selected uniformly at random across all entries. The winner is notified via in-app notification and the email address on their Futpools account within 48 hours. Winner has 7 days to claim the prize; unclaimed prizes are forfeit."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Después de cerradas las entradas, se selecciona un ganador de manera uniformemente aleatoria entre todas las entradas. El ganador es notificado por notificación en la app y por el correo electrónico de su cuenta Futpools en un plazo de 48 horas. El ganador tiene 7 días para reclamar el premio; los premios no reclamados se pierden."
          }
        }
      }
    },
